# 7. あの夜の火は、今も

Akito: Let's start, Ken.
Ken: Okay.
Ken: (He seems much calmer today... I'm not sensing any of his usual anxiety today.)
Ken: I take it you figured something out...?
Ken: In that case, I'll start us off today. Ready?
Akito: Yes!
Ken: (I see... He's focusing on the way I'm singing.)
Ken: (Then, I'll need to put on a good performance for him...)
Ken: ♪————————!!
Akito: ...!
Akito: (Again, he really is something else...)
Akito: (Hearing Ken sing just fills me up with so much excitement. I can feel the pulse in my fingers.)
Akito: (On top of that, lately... He's been singing just for me.)
Akito: (This has to be some kind of miracle...)
Akito: (Feel his song. Let it flow through you...)
Akito: (Listen to the man who ignited an eternal flame in you.)
Ken: ♪————————!!
Akito: (You got the blood pumping in my heart. You. No one else.)
Akito: (It's because of you that I'm stood here right now.)
Akito: (Nervousness, excitement, happiness... All these emotions I should have felt being around you. I should never have suppressed them like I did.)
Akito: (Which is why I'm going to feel them all now, completely. Everything you gave me.)
Akito: ♪——————!!
Akito: (I'm gonna turn that into my strength and surpass you!!)
Ken: You finally got it...
Ken: (You have a habit of overthinking things. That's why you need to make things more simple for yourself.)
Ken: (Happiness, sadness, anger... Everything you've felt... That all needs to become your fuel.)
Ken: (It needs to drive your singing.)
Akito: ♪————————!!
Akito: Huff... Huff... Huff...
Ken: That was good.
Ken: But... We're not done yet.
Akito: Huh...?
Ken: ♪————————!!!!
Akito: (...! That singing...!)
Akito: (He sang like this at RAD WEEKEND...!)
Akito: (He really means it now...!)
Ken: ♪————————!!!!
Akito: (No... What am I doing...? I thought I was ready for this.)
Akito: (My hands... They're shaking...)
Akito: (Am I really going to be able to...?)
Akito: (No, stop... Don't say that...!)
Akito: (Burn...! Burn it all!)
Akito: (Burn everything that you have inside of you!)
Akito: (Say, Ken...)
Akito: (You gave me so much when I saw you at RAD WEEKEND.)
Akito: (Things were really hard at first, and I felt like giving up more times than I wanna admit.)
Akito: (But...)
Akito: (Even then...)
Akito: (They decided to stand by my side.)
Akito: (And... Even after gaining and losing so much... Even after being beaten to a pulp like this, I can keep going...)
Akito: (Because I'm never going to forget that night!)
Akito: ♪————————————————!!!!
Akito: (So, Ken.)
Akito: (The flame you lit inside of me that night is still burning strong.)
Akito: (And I can't thank you enough for that.)
Akito: (Which is why...)
Akito: (I'm gonna surpass you.)
Akito: (That's right... Take everything away, and this is what's left.)
Akito: (That desire. The one that brought me this far.)
Akito: (Ken.)
Akito: (I'm gonna surpass you. I'm gonna surpass RAD WEEKEND, and then I'll go even further!!!)
Akito: ♪————————————————!!!!
Ken: It's getting hot in here...
Akito: Huff... Huff... Huff...!
Akito: (No, whoa... I'm having trouble standing...!)
Ken: You did it, Akito.
Akito: What...?
Ken: You just convinced me.
Ken: I want to witness the moment you and your team surpass us.
Akito: Thank you!
Ken: Alright, you've all put in plenty of effort until today.
Ken: You've all reached a good level. I say the time is ripe.
Ken: Akito.
Akito: Yes!
Ken: It's time for you to lead the charge. Are you ready?
Akito: Yes. I'm ready to go whenever.
An: You know, a part of me still wants us all to sing together since this is our big return...
An: But I know you're gonna really ignite everyone, Akito!
Kohane: Me too...! I know you can do it, Shinonome!
Toya: Akito.
Toya: Your hard work will pay off... I firmly believe that.
Akito: Thanks, you guys.
Ken: Give it everything you've got. We'll be watching from across the street so that we don't get in your way.
Akito: Okay.
Akito: Then, let's go.
